==================== JS console ======================
create a new build system and paste it inside.

{
  "cmd": ["/usr/local/bin/node", "$file"],
  "selector": "source.js"
}
Windows usersâ€¦

{
  "cmd": ["node", "$file", "$file_base_name"],
  "working_dir": "${project_path:${folder}}",
  "selector": "*.js"
}


Save it as JavaScript.sublime-build

